summary: Completed comprehensive frontend testing of HiveMind Marketing website. All core features working correctly including navigation, forms, responsive design, and branding elements.
passed_tests: Homepage loads with hero section and HiveMind branding
Two CTA buttons visible and functional ('For Brands' and 'For Creators')
Logo carousel visible and animating with placeholder brand logos
Navigation to Brands page works correctly
Brands page displays hero image, 3 benefit cards, and form section
Form placeholder shows 'FORMLINKHERE' text as specified
Form submission displays success confirmation message
Back button navigates correctly to homepage
Navigation to Creators page works correctly
Creators page displays hero image, 3 benefit cards, and form section
Header logo links back to homepage from all pages
Warm peach background color (#fff3e7) applied correctly
Primary color (#f48d2d) used consistently throughout design
Caprasimo font used for headings, DM Sans for body text
Mobile responsive design - CTA buttons stack vertically
All navigation and form interactions work on mobile devices
Professional design with proper spacing and visual hierarchy
